cobalt strike can generate these reports based on recorded activity
    activity report: overall timeline of post-exploitation activity
    hosts report: summarizes info found on each host (e.g. creds, services, etc.)
    IOC report: includes analysis of C2's traffic profile, domains, file hashes
    sessions report: summarizes post-exploitation activity by session
    social engineering report: activity from the built-in spear phishing capabilities
    TTP report: maps activity with MITRE ATT&CK

these can be generated from the 'Reporting' menu

typical red team report structure
    executive summary
    goals & scenario
    attack narative
    observations & recommendations
    conclusion

